Nihon Unicom to buy back 310 , 000 shares . Nihon Unicom Corp , a specialised futures trader , said on Thursday it has decided to buy back 310 , 000 of its own shares to introduce a stock option scheme . The amount of the share repurchase would be 500 million yen , the company said . The decision must be approved by a shareholders ' meeting scheduled for June 27 . The stock options will be offered to 15 board directors and 32 executives . The repurchase will be carried out from July 1 , 1998 , to September 30 , 2000 , Nihon Unicom said . 
